<div class="container">
  
  <div class="featurette">
    <h2 class="featurette-heading">Welcome to MASSOLIT</h2>
      <p class="lead">We are the first online education platform that specialises in the humanities. You can find everything here - from literature to history, philosophy to politics, and much, much more. 
        <%= link_to "Browse our courses", courses_path %>
      <br>
    </div>


