      <p class="lead">Our content has been designed to help students make that first step towards higher education. Content is wider ranging, and delivered in a lecture format - just as would be the case at university. If you're a student and want to see what we can offer,
        <%= link_to "sign up here", new_subscriber_registration_path(:job => 'student') %>
      <br>
  </div>

    <div class="featurette">
    <h2 class="featurette-heading">... and learn from the best...</h2>
      <p class="lead">
        All our courses are designed and presented by academics from the world's very best universities, including Oxford and Cambridge. Want to find out more? <%= link_to "Get in touch!", "mailto:chris@massolit.co.uk?Subject=MASSOLIT: Tell Me More" %>
    </div>

  <div class="featurette">
    <h2 class="featurette-heading">... with powerful analytics</h2>
      <p class="lead">Schools that sign up to MASSOLIT gain access to our powerful analytics tools, which tell you how much your students are using the site and engaging with content. We're able to customise any part of our analytics package to suit your needs. If you're a teacher and want to find out more, <%= link_to "sign up", new_subscriber_registration_path(:job => 'student') %> or 
      <%= link_to "get in touch!", "mailto:chris@massolit.co.uk?Subject=MASSOLIT: Tell Me More" %>
      <br>
  </div>


</div>